description.narrative: UNICEF Country Office efforts have been focused on providing targeted and tailored support to the COVID-19 pandemic response. In particular, the COVID-19 pandemic has posed significant strain on Cross-Sectoral Operations. The CO has been engaged in the overall COVID-19 response in coordination and collaboration with other UN Agencies. UNICEF has conducted risk communication as well as procurement of hygiene supplies, personal protective equipment (PPE) and medical equipment with the objective of strengthening the national health system for the response. | Status:Met | As-of Date:17/12/2020
